short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A tool to generate Discord timestamps.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Discord Timestamp Generator is a simple and efficient tool designed to help you generate precise timestamps for Discord messages. Whether you're scheduling events, logging activities, or just need a quick timestamp, this extension makes it easy.

Features:
- Generate timestamps in various formats (short time, long time, short date, long date, etc.)
- Copy timestamps to clipboard with a single click
- Reset to current system time
- User-friendly interface
- Developed by Noman Mohammad

Install now and streamline your Discord timestamp generation!
